TỔNG KẾT PHẦN HỌC
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  • Root User & Elevated Permissions
      • /etc/sudoers, sudoers.d (visudo)
      • su, sudo, sshd_config (disable root login)

  • Monitoring Resource Utilization
      • sar, vmstat, free, df

  • Backups and Compression
      • tar (archive, gzip, bzip2, xz)
      • rsync (copy/sync)

  • Common System Applications
      • Apache (httpd), Postfix, NTP/Chrony
      • Config files: httpd.conf, main.cf, ntp.conf, chrony.conf

  • Viewing and Managing Log Files
      • /var/log/messages (Red Hat), /var/log/syslog (Debian)
      • journalctl, logrotate

  • Configuring Network Interfaces
      • ifcfg (Red Hat), interfaces (Debian), nmcli

  • Managing Network Access and Security
      • firewalld, firewall-cmd
      • sshd_config (AllowUsers, AllowGroups)

  • Runlevels and Targets
      • SysV Init runlevels vs Systemd targets
      • systemctl get-default, set-default, isolate

  • Basic SELinux Implementation and Tools
      • Modes: enforcing, permissive, disabled
      • Context: user:role:type:range
      • semanage, getenforce, setsebool, chcon, restorecon


KẾT LUẬN
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Phần System Administration Fundamentals trang bị kiến thức toàn diện để quản 
  trị Linux server: root, monitoring, backup, applications, logs, networking, 
  security, targets, SELinux.

  Hãy ôn quiz và thực hành lab để củng cố.


